name: cat with caffeine
description:
I used to have 11 cats in my house,

I named them all cats with Coffee's name.
sometimes cats can inspire you, give you ideas, recharge your energy.
just like a cup of coffee

this one is Doppio I accidentally take a picture of her weird expression like this (you can see her on my IG / Twitter) I don't think she knows she is a cat until now.

now doppio lives in the blockchain (of course she is still alive)
I want you guys to have it. just like a cup of coffee from me.
